ORCH -[#D2691E,thickness=3]down-> AG5 : <b>⑤Policy</b>\n2.1s
ORCH -[#0066CC,thickness=2]down-> AG6 : <b>⑥Fraud</b>\n0.68s
ORCH -[#0066CC,thickness=3]down-> AG7 : <b>⑦Decision</b>\n0.85s

' Agents to MCP Tools
AG1 .down.> T1 : use
AG2 .down.> T2 : use
AG4 .down.> T3 : use
AG6 .down.> T4 : use

' Agents to Model Serving Infrastructure
AG1 -[#228B22,thickness=2]-> SM_RF : classify
